text: Through the Years/A Traves de los Años is a album by American singer Selena. The album contained an unreleased song called "Feelings". The song was recorded when Selena was only 7 years old. The album peaked at number 28 on the Top Latin Albums Chart and was certified Gold by the RIAA. ==Track listing== # Feelings (unreleased) # Como Te Quiero Yo A Ti # Tu Solamente Tu # Tu No Sabes # Que # Sukiyaki # Amame, Quiereme # Yo Te Amo # Ya Ves # Yo Te Sigo Queriendo # Amame # No Debes Jugar # La Llamada # Fotos Y Recuerdos # Ya No # Dreaming of You # Puede Ser ==Charts== === Weekly charts === Chart (2007) Peak position US Top Latin Albums 28 US Top Regional Mexican Albums 13 Chart (2012) Peak position == References == Category:Selena albums Category:2007 albums Category:Spanish-language albums
